                        <hi rend="rubric">፨</hi>
                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11905GabraM">
                           <hi rend="rubric">ገብረ፡ ማርያም፡</hi>
                        </persName> ወጸሐፊሁኒ፡ ወእምኵሉ፡ እቀብኒ፡ <add place="above">ለ</add>ኃጥዕ፡ ገብርኪ<hi rend="rubric">፨</hi>
                        <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12977WaldaTaklaHaymanot">Walda Takla Hāymānot<hi rend="rubric">ወልደ፡ <del rend="strikethrough">ወ</del>ተክለ፡
